OL,3,CNurses threaten industrial action
OL,4,Cballot after pay offer rejected
OL,6,FNurses in England could be balloted on
OL,7,Findustrial action if the government
OL,8,Fdoes not reach agreement on investment
OL,9,Fin the workforce over the summer, the
OL,10,FRoyal College of Nursing (RCN) has
OL,11,Fwarned.
OL,13,FIt comes as nurses overwhelmingly
OL,14,Fvoted to a reject a 3.6% pay offer.
OL,16,FThe RCN said nurses are "deeply
OL,17,Fundervalued" and the pay award was
OL,18,F"not enough" to reverse widespread
OL,19,Fvacancies, stunted career progression
OL,20,Fand years of pay erosion.
