OL,3,CNurses threaten industrial action
OL,4,Cballot after pay offer rejected
OL,6,FThey are now urging the government to
OL,7,Fnegotiate reforms on the "outdated pay
OL,8,Fstructure" to avoid formal escalation.
OL,10,FIt follows a five-day walkout by
OL,11,Fthousands of resident doctors,
OL,12,Fformerly known as junior doctors,
OL,13,Fwhich came to an end on Wednesday.
OL,15,FThe Department of Health and Social
OL,16,FCare (DHSC) said the government
OL,17,F"hugely" values the work of nurses,
OL,18,Fbut stressed the profession has had
OL,19,F"two above-inflation pay rises".
