OL,6,FHowever, RCN General Secretary and
OL,7,FChief Executive, Professor Nicola
OL,8,FRanger, said: "My profession feels
OL,9,Fdeeply undervalued and that is why
OL,10,Frecord numbers are telling the
OL,11,Fgovernment to wake up, sense the
OL,12,Furgency here and do what's right by
OL,13,Fthem and by patients.
OL,15,F"Record numbers have delivered this
OL,16,Fverdict on a broken system that holds
OL,17,Fback nursing pay and careers and
OL,18,Fhampers the NHS."
