OL,6,FProf Ranger continued: "We deliver the
OL,7,Fvast majority of care in every service
OL,8,Fand deserve to be valued for all our
OL,9,Fskill, knowledge and experience.
OL,11,F"To avoid formal escalation, the
OL,12,FGovernment must be true to its word
OL,13,Fand negotiate on reforms of the
OL,14,Foutdated pay structure which traps
OL,15,Fnursing staff at the same band their
OL,16,Fentire career."
OL,18,FA record-breaking number of 170,000
OL,19,Fstaff voted on the pay award, with 91%
OL,20,Fvoting to reject it, the RCN said.
