OL,6,FNurses in Wales and Northern Ireland
OL,7,Fwere consulted on the same pay award
OL,8,Fand voted to reject it, according to
OL,9,Fthe RCN.
OL,11,FA DHSC spokesperson said: "After
OL,12,Freceiving two above-inflation pay
OL,13,Frises from this government, new full-
OL,14,Ftime nurses will earn #30,000 in basic
OL,15,Fpay for the first time this year, so
OL,16,Fit's disappointing that RCN members
OL,17,Fare dissatisfied with this year's pay
OL,18,Frise.
