OL,6,F"We hugely value the work of nurses,
OL,7,Fand through our ten year health plan,
OL,8,Fwe are rebuilding the NHS for the
OL,9,Fbenefit of patients and staff, and
OL,10,Fensuring nursing remains an attractive
OL,11,Fcareer choice.
OL,13,F"This government is clear we can't
OL,14,Fmove any further on headline pay but
OL,15,Fwill work with the RCN to improve
OL,16,Ftheir major concerns, including pay
OL,17,Fstructure reform, concerns on career
OL,18,Fprogression and wider working
OL,19,Fconditions."
