OL,6,FNurses staged unprecedented industrial
OL,7,Faction over pay in 2022 and 2023.
OL,9,FIn June 2023, the threat of more
OL,10,Fstrikes ended because a ballot on
OL,11,Ffurther walkouts failed to meet the
OL,12,Flegal threshold of 50%.
OL,14,FThe RCN warning over a potential
OL,15,Fballot for industrial action follows a
OL,16,Ffive-day walkout by resident doctors
OL,17,Fin England.
