OL,6,FHealth secretary Wes Streeting has
OL,7,Fsince written to the British Medical
OL,8,FAssociation (BMA) saying he is willing
OL,9,Fto meet the union's resident doctors
OL,10,Fcommittee to resume talks.
OL,12,FHowever, he warned that resident
OL,13,Fdoctors have squandered the
OL,14,F"considerable goodwill" they had with
OL,15,Fgovernment after the strike.
